{"tid":1071801,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"買樓好易架姐，係廢青先無首期","createTime":"2019-03-21T14:55:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-12T04:21:53.000Z","uid":27415,"like":40,"dislike":41,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"a8eba61199def97092169c0f530b34e08ebbac57","tid":1071801,"uid":27415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T14:55:03.000Z","msg":"我屌你啦 政府 ，屌埋你班議員，日日鳩up轉移視線，呃飯食。係香港做中產就最慘啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有無做過咩實際嘢去阻止樓市價格上升到不合理水平啊屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n香港人唔需要福利啊屌！！！<br />\nD福利落曬D大陸150隻既袋<br />\n<br />\n我地需要既係限制！<br />\n（1）需要租金管制，先可以壓抑樓市<br />\n（2）需要限制新樓既建築面積，唔可以太細<br />\n太細唔人道，二來可以防止發展商不合理推高樓價<br />\n<br />\n例如：佢知道你負擔到600-1000萬，如果唔限制面積，佢會起100呎樓賣700萬，咁樣一來又推高呎價。<br />\n<br />\n黑心至極！"},{"pid":"c4e721d1be17c37f369d4bb60899487feb704fbb","tid":1071801,"uid":27415,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T14:55:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a735e3e51bd7b914292e236cd697e48a8b4ce685","tid":1071801,"uid":27415,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T14:55:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8370cf84c217575b3eda096a3d47efe0004bc4b","tid":1071801,"uid":27415,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T14:57:45.000Z","msg":"800萬買300呎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50e3407ceb24967033e75dfbb960a536d9847db4","tid":1071801,"uid":27415,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T15:00:39.000Z","msg":"屯門菁雋「龍床盤」 128呎細絕新盤 網民﹕衰過公屋 但平過兩球都搶爆<br />\n<br /